data.name: label1.Text
data.value:
Patient registration is the process of collecting information like Name, Age, Address, Gender and Mobile number etc to perform several administrative functions like tracking Patient visits, keep the records of the fee paid by patients, Maintaining the Patient's Medical Test reports etc.
This user who is collecting the information must remain calm and efficient since his or her work is often performed in a fast-paced environment where time is of the essence.
